The paper proposes a new algorithm for training TSK fuzzy systems for regression problems, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The proposed algorithm involves regularization, drop rule, and AdaBound, which are optimization techniques commonly used in neural networks and deep learning (cs.NE). The paper also proposes a rule-pruning algorithm, which is a technique commonly used in fuzzy systems and control theory (cs.SY, cs.FL). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE, followed by cs.SY and cs.FL.
